.m-product#m-product
    p._title.d-ex__title Enquiry form

    form
        ._info
            ._img-wrap
                img(src="img/product-img.jpg")

            ._info-wrap
                p._author.m-product__info-text Katia Kesic
                p._name.m-product__info-text Let Me Tell You What Happens Next, 2019
                p._desc.m-product__info-text Underglaze on stoneware clay, chain, glass eye
                p._size.m-product__info-text 34 x 33 x 33 cm

        ._item
            label(for="name")._label Name*
            input(type="text" name="name" id="name" required)._input.m-product__input-item

        ._item
            label(for="name")._label Email*
            input(type="email" name="email" id="email" required)._input.m-product__input-item

        ._item
            label(for="phone")._label Phone
            input(type="number" name="phone" id="phone")._input.m-product__input-item

        ._item
            label(for="message")._label Message
            textarea(type="text" name="message" id="message")._input.m-product__input-item.m-product__message

        ._item.m-product__item-radios
            p._label Receive
                |
                | newsletters*

            ._radios.m-product__input-item
                label
                    input(type="radio" name="newsletters")
                    span Yes

                label
                    input(type="radio" name="newsletters")
                    span No

        button._button.button(type="submit") Send enquiry


        p._bottom In order to respond to your enquiry, we will process the personal data you have supplied in accordance with our privacy policy (available on request). You can unsubscribe or change your preferences at any time by clicking the link in our emails.

